snippet.title: [EN] ICE Temple Trailer | Infokub Arcade
snippet.description:
Welcome to the ICE Temple

Are you ready to slide ?
Release in April 2021


The game will be available for Windows and Android and you can already play the demo !


Play the demo on Itch
https://infokubarcade.itch.io/ice-temple
Play the demo on Gamejolt
https://gamejolt.com/games/ice-temple/557610
